Package puzzle.model

Class PuzzleState

java.lang.Object
puzzle.model.PuzzleState
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable, State, TwoPhaseMoveState
public class PuzzleState extends Object implements TwoPhaseMoveState
The PuzzleState class represents the state of the puzzle game board. It implements the State and TwoPhaseMoveState interfaces.
